Win10_English_x64.iso <br />root@desktop:/mnt# <br />root@desktop:/mnt# du -b 3/Win10_English_x64.iso <br />4556128256\t3/Win10_English_x64.iso<br />root@desktop:/mnt# <br />root@desktop:/mnt# du -b 4/Win10_English_x64.iso <br />4556128256\t4/Win10_English_x64.iso<br />root@desktop:/mnt#","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/816648","replies":27,"created_ts":1637328281,"created":"21:24:41","title":"du 命令报告的文件大小错误，这种情况是 u 盘坏了还是 du 命令的问题？","author":"kgdb00","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kgdb00","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a5fb38dc1a69984a16c1b1c007b68172?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":816604,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"难顶","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/816604","replies":25,"created_ts":1637314454,"created":"17:34:14","title":"前几天说键盘进饮料坏了，淘宝找了一家店修，刚刚收到说主板腐蚀了，不保证能修好………","author":"zxCoder","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zxCoder","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb4e/991a/457207_mini.png?m=1635067942"}]